00:14:05.180 --> 00:14:07.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Ah!
- [laughing]</b></Default>

c0000325
00:14:07.390 --> 00:14:10.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fireworks screeching]</b></Default>

c0000326
00:14:13.810 --> 00:14:16.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You haven't asked me
about anything, Kunimi.</b></Default>

c0000327
00:14:16.440 --> 00:14:17.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000328
00:14:18.270 --> 00:14:19.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- About all of this.</b></Default>

c0000329
00:14:20.280 --> 00:14:21.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I mean, I was definitely
wondering what the hell</b></Default>

c0000330
00:14:21.860 --> 00:14:23.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was going on when Sakuta called.</b></Default>

c0000331
00:14:23.530 --> 00:14:25.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But when I got there and saw you</b></Default>

c0000332
00:14:25.160 --> 00:14:26.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>breaking down like that,</b></Default>

c0000333
00:14:26.320 --> 00:14:27.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it didn't matter anymore.</b></Default>

c0000334
00:14:30.330 --> 00:14:31.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[stammers]
- Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000335
00:14:31.700 --> 00:14:34.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Aww, dammit.
I lost.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:14:34.710 --> 00:14:36.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whatever. Maybe we'll get
a good view from here</b></Default>

c0000337
00:14:37.040 --> 00:14:40.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for next week's fireworks
festival in Enoshima.</b></Default>

c0000338
00:14:40.210 --> 00:14:42.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why don't we all watch
it together again?</b></Default>

c0000339
00:14:42.220 --> 00:14:43.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Don't you have plans to go</b></Default>

c0000340
00:14:43.550 --> 00:14:45.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with that cute girlfriend
of yours?</b></Default>

c0000341
00:14:45.090 --> 00:14:48.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Eh, we're totally in
the middle of a big fight.</b></Default>

c0000342
00:14:48.180 --> 00:14:49.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And what about you?
You're probably going</b></Default>

c0000343
00:14:49.890 --> 00:14:51.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with Sakurajima, aren't you?</b></Default>

c0000344
00:14:51.350 --> 00:14:52.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Thanks to her agency,</b></Default>

c0000345
00:14:52.810 --> 00:14:54.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we're currently prohibited
from going on dates.</b></Default>

c0000346
00:14:54.980 --> 00:14:56.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hah, it's tough having
a famous girlfriend.</b></Default>

c0000347
00:14:57.270 --> 00:14:58.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Futaba?</b></Default>

c0000348
00:14:58.520 --> 00:14:59.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I don't have anything
going on.</b></Default>

c0000349
00:14:59.820 --> 00:15:01.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then that's that.</b></Default>

c0000350
00:15:01.480 --> 00:15:03.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[yawns]</b></Default>

c0000351
00:15:04.360 --> 00:15:06.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold on.
Is it getting brighter?</b></Default>

c0000352
00:15:06.280 --> 00:15:07.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000353
00:15:07.570 --> 00:15:08.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've never pulled an all-nighter</b></Default>

c0000354
00:15:08.830 --> 00:15:10.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>like this before, ever.</b></Default>

c0000355
00:15:11.080 --> 00:15:12.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What in the world am I doing?</b></Default>

c0000356
00:15:13.620 --> 00:15:15.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're doing something stupid,
obviously.</b></Default>

c0000357
00:15:15.960 --> 00:15:17.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- This really wasn't
the smartest idea, was it?</b></Default>

c0000358
00:15:19.000 --> 00:15:21.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [giggles]</b></Default>

c0000359
00:15:21.550 --> 00:15:23.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't help but think
how perfect it would be</b></Default>

c0000360
00:15:23.510 --> 00:15:24.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you were both girls.</b></Default>

c0000361
00:15:27.220 --> 00:15:28.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The train should
be moving by now.</b></Default>

c0000362
00:15:28.970 --> 00:15:31.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, that was fun.
See ya.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:15:31.470 --> 00:15:32.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Bye.</b></Default>

c0000364
00:15:32.810 --> 00:15:35.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

c0000365
00:15:36.810 --> 00:15:39.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Azusagawa.
- Are you still scared?</b></Default>

c0000366
00:15:39.270 --> 00:15:40.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can stay with you again today.</b></Default>

c0000367
00:15:40.980 --> 00:15:42.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm good on that front.</b></Default>

c0000368
00:15:42.480 --> 00:15:44.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But my other self
has me worried.</b></Default>

c0000369
00:15:44.490 --> 00:15:46.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's been going through it
a lot worse than I am.</b></Default>

c0000370
00:15:46.950 --> 00:15:48.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm.
- She absolutely hates me</b></Default>

c0000371
00:15:48.700 --> 00:15:51.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to her core so I really
need your help.</b></Default>

c0000372
00:15:51.740 --> 00:15:53.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Take care of my other self
for me.</b></Default>

c0000373
00:15:54.290 --> 00:15:55.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please.</b></Default>

c0000374
00:15:55.790 --> 00:15:57.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

c0000375
00:15:57.540 --> 00:15:58.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door closes]</b></Default>

c0000376
00:16:00.880 --> 00:16:02.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Welcome back.</b></Default>

c0000377
00:16:02.550 --> 00:16:04.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, what's up?
- You must be exhausted.</b></Default>

c0000378
00:16:06.470 --> 00:16:07.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Got this.</b></Default>

c0000379
00:16:07.840 --> 00:16:09.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She said that she deleted
the account.</b></Default>

c0000380
00:16:09.840 --> 00:16:10.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think she's done
with that stuff.</b></Default>

c0000381
00:16:11.050 --> 00:16:12.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Ah.</b></Default>

c0000382
00:16:12.470 --> 00:16:14.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'll fill you in on all
the details later.</b></Default>

c0000383
00:16:14.810 --> 00:16:16.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now I
think I'll sleep.</b></Default>

c0000384
00:16:16.810 --> 00:16:17.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Night.</b></Default>

c0000385
00:16:20.230 --> 00:16:21.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000386
00:16:23.110 --> 00:16:26.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind blowing]</b></Default>

c0000387
00:16:29.860 --> 00:16:32.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groaning]</b></Default>

c0000388
00:16:32.830 --> 00:16:33.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000389
00:16:35.660 --> 00:16:37.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, good morning to you,
big brother.</b></Default>

c0000390
00:16:38.370 --> 00:16:40.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Good morning to you,
too, Kaede.</b></Default>

c0000391
00:16:41.330 --> 00:16:43.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Futaba in my room?
- Nope.</b></Default>

c0000392
00:16:43.460 --> 00:16:45.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She hasn't come back yet.
- Huh?</b></Default>

c0000393
00:16:45.420 --> 00:16:46.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did she go out?</b></Default>

c0000394
00:16:47.050 --> 00:16:49.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh-huh, pretty much right
after you got back home.</b></Default>

c0000395
00:16:49.300 --> 00:16:51.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She said that she was going
to go shopping.</b></Default>

c0000396
00:16:51.090 --> 00:16:52.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She went shopping?</b></Default>

c0000397
00:16:53.390 --> 00:16:54.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000398
00:16:56.640 --> 00:16:59.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[buttons clicking]</b></Default>

c0000399
00:16:59.730 --> 00:17:00.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone trilling]
[cell phone ringing]</b></Default>

c0000400
00:17:00.730 --> 00:17:01.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both gasping]</b></Default>

c0000401
00:17:02.810 --> 00:17:05.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Dammit! She seriously left
her phone here?</b></Default>

c0000402
00:17:09.110 --> 00:17:10.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000403
00:17:10.740 --> 00:17:12.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Man, this is the worst!
[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000404
00:17:15.280 --> 00:17:16.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What's wrong?</b></Default>

c0000405
00:17:16.580 --> 00:17:18.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Futaba's gone missing.</b></Default>

c0000406
00:17:18.330 --> 00:17:20.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I went home and passed out
and when I woke up she was gone</b></Default>

c0000407
00:17:20.790 --> 00:17:22.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>along with all her stuff!</b></Default>

c0000408
00:17:22.080 --> 00:17:23.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Let me get one thing out
of the way.</b></Default>

c0000409
00:17:23.960 --> 00:17:26.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We haven't returned
to being one person yet.</b></Default>

c0000410
00:17:26.170 --> 00:17:28.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Any idea about where
she might have gone?</b></Default>

c0000411
00:17:28.710 --> 00:17:30.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, if it was me...</b></Default>

c0000412
00:17:34.010 --> 00:17:36.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Ah, this is such a pain in
the ass!</b></Default>

c0000413
00:17:36.100 --> 00:17:37.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's so tedious.</b></Default>

c0000414
00:17:37.270 --> 00:17:39.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Actually, Futaba,
you're tedious!</b></Default>

c0000415
00:17:46.110 --> 00:17:46.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[breathing heavily]
- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000416
00:17:47.020 --> 00:17:48.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [breathing heavily]</b></Default>

c0000417
00:17:49.030 --> 00:17:51.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Azusagawa.
Why are you...</b></Default>

c0000418
00:17:52.450 --> 00:17:53.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales sharply]</b></Default>

c0000419
00:17:54.240 --> 00:17:56.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Man, well, that sure
was horrible.</b></Default>

c0000420
00:17:56.740 --> 00:17:59.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yesterday,
or rather this morning,</b></Default>

c0000421
00:17:59.410 --> 00:18:01.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there was something I really
needed to talk to you about.</b></Default>

c0000422
00:18:01.750 --> 00:18:03.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What?
- Next week.</b></Default>

c0000423
00:18:03.790 --> 00:18:05.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wanna see the fireworks?
- Huh?</b></Default>

c0000424
00:18:05.670 --> 00:18:07.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The fireworks festival
at Enoshima,</b></Default>

c0000425
00:18:07.840 --> 00:18:10.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>where we went last year.
Kunimi said he'd come with us.</b></Default>

c0000426
00:18:11.300 --> 00:18:13.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- W--Well, I--
- You're coming, too, right?</b></Default>

c0000427
00:18:14.430 --> 00:18:15.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm not.</b></Default>

c0000428
00:18:15.800 --> 00:18:17.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You already got plans
or something?</b></Default>

c0000429
00:18:17.470 --> 00:18:18.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm just done.</b></Default>

c0000430
00:18:18.850 --> 00:18:20.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm going to disappear.</b></Default>

c0000431
00:18:20.310 --> 00:18:21.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000432
00:18:21.600 --> 00:18:23.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'll disappear
from your sight.</b></Default>

c0000433
00:18:24.150 --> 00:18:26.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll disappear
from this entire city.</b></Default>

c0000434
00:18:26.150 --> 00:18:27.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Why would you say that?</b></Default>

c0000435
00:18:28.520 --> 00:18:29.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- There's no reason
for the world</b></Default>

c0000436
00:18:29.980 --> 00:18:31.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to have two Rio Futabas.</b></Default>

c0000437
00:18:32.780 --> 00:18:34.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And it's painfully clear
that my other self</b></Default>

c0000438
00:18:34.860 --> 00:18:37.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is much better
at being Rio Futaba than I am.</b></Default>

c0000439
00:18:37.870 --> 00:18:39.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's really found
her place here.</b></Default>

c0000440
00:18:40.290 --> 00:18:43.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Everything would resolve itself
if I was simply not here.</b></Default>

c0000441
00:18:43.250 --> 00:18:45.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, I'm sorry,
but that answer is incorrect.</b></Default>

c0000442
00:18:45.580 --> 00:18:47.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No, I'm 100% right.</b></Default>

c0000443
00:18:47.250 --> 00:18:48.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Couldn't be more wrong.</b></Default>

c0000444
00:18:48.750 --> 00:18:50.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your entire argument's baseless.</b></Default>

c0000445
00:18:50.670 --> 00:18:53.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If that's true
then that picture--</b></Default>

c0000446
00:18:53.550 --> 00:18:55.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what else could I think
after seeing a picture</b></Default>

c0000447
00:18:55.340 --> 00:18:57.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of everything I've ever wanted?</b></Default>

c0000448
00:18:57.350 --> 00:18:59.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There isn't a place left
in this world for me!</b></Default>

c0000449
00:18:59.970 --> 00:19:01.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no more need for me.</b></Default>

c0000450
00:19:01.770 --> 00:19:03.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Both you and Kunimi will be fine
as long as you still have</b></Default>

c0000451
00:19:04.020 --> 00:19:05.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>my other self, right?
[sniffs]</b></Default>

c0000452
00:19:05.900 --> 00:19:07.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawa,
you're so insensitive!</b></Default>

c0000453
00:19:07.900 --> 00:19:10.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Idiot, you're saying that now
after all this?</b></Default>

c0000454
00:19:10.480 --> 00:19:12.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- Don't act like me</b></Default>

c0000455
00:19:12.400 --> 00:19:15.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>being insensitive is news.
You've known that forever.</b></Default>

c0000456
00:19:15.450 --> 00:19:18.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anyway, we're meeting
at Kuganuma-Kaigan Station</b></Default>

c0000457
00:19:18.240 --> 00:19:19.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at 6:30 on the 19th.</b></Default>

c0000458
00:19:19.830 --> 00:19:21.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's all I have left to say.</b></Default>

c0000459
00:19:21.490 --> 00:19:22.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000460
00:19:23.410 --> 00:19:24.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000461
00:19:25.580 --> 00:19:26.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]
- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000462
00:19:27.000 --> 00:19:28.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thuds]
Azusagawa!</b></Default>

c0000463
00:19:34.840 --> 00:19:36.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- Good morning.</b></Default>

c0000464
00:19:36.630 --> 00:19:38.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is your fault
for running around like</b></Default>

c0000465
00:19:38.970 --> 00:19:40.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a madman in the pouring rain.</b></Default>

c0000466
00:19:41.470 --> 00:19:43.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>According to the test results,
you're fine.</b></Default>

c0000467
00:19:43.390 --> 00:19:44.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000468
00:19:44.680 --> 00:19:46.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Why do you look so captivated?</b></Default>

c0000469
00:19:46.890 --> 00:19:50.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- A super beautiful
upperclassman just appeared so--</b></Default>

c0000470
00:19:50.610 --> 00:19:52.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Since you're acting like this,
you must be okay.</b></Default>

c0000471
00:19:53.030 --> 00:19:55.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So how did you know
to show up here, anyway?</b></Default>

c0000472
00:19:56.070 --> 00:19:57.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Futaba called me
after you passed out.</b></Default>

c0000473
00:19:59.820 --> 00:20:01.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
Azusagawa.</b></Default>

c0000474
00:20:02.540 --> 00:20:04.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I caused you real trouble,
Futaba.</b></Default>

c0000475
00:20:04.540 --> 00:20:07.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No kidding.
You're so unfair.</b></Default>

c0000476
00:20:07.960 --> 00:20:10.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In you pass out in that kind
of place, I can't leave you.</b></Default>

c0000477
00:20:10.330 --> 00:20:12.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If that's true then maybe
it's a good thing.</b></Default>

c0000478
00:20:13.840 --> 00:20:15.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Azusagawa.</b></Default>

c0000479
00:20:15.880 --> 00:20:17.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Listen, I--
- If it's something about how</b></Default>

c0000480
00:20:17.590 --> 00:20:19.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you're no longer needed here,</b></Default>

c0000481
00:20:19.140 --> 00:20:20.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or how everything
will be bunnies and rainbows</b></Default>

c0000482
00:20:21.010 --> 00:20:22.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you fade away,</b></Default>

c0000483
00:20:22.260 --> 00:20:23.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or how you can't help
but be scared</b></Default>

c0000484
00:20:23.850 --> 00:20:25.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and you don't think there's
anything you can do about it,</b></Default>

c0000485
00:20:25.720 --> 00:20:27.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't wanna hear it again.</b></Default>

c0000486
00:20:27.140 --> 00:20:29.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm done listening
to tedious stuff like that.</b></Default>

c0000487
00:20:29.310 --> 00:20:30.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales]</b></Default>

c0000488
00:20:30.600 --> 00:20:32.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's all right
if you hate yourself.</b></Default>

c0000489
00:20:32.190 --> 00:20:33.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're allowed to feel that way.</b></Default>

c0000490
00:20:33.820 --> 00:20:35.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And it's not just you.</b></Default>

c0000491
00:20:35.440 --> 00:20:37.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just tell myself
it is what it is</b></Default>

c0000492
00:20:37.280 --> 00:20:38.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I keep on going.</b></Default>

c0000493
00:20:40.200 --> 00:20:42.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
That's very you.</b></Default>

c0000494
00:20:42.830 --> 00:20:45.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Isn't this normally the part
where someone would say,</b></Default>

c0000495
00:20:45.370 --> 00:20:47.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"Don't worry, you can work on
liking yourself over time,"</b></Default>

c0000496
00:20:47.830 --> 00:20:49.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or, "What do you mean?</b></Default>

c0000497
00:20:49.330 --> 00:20:51.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are tons of awesome things
about you, Futaba?"</b></Default>

c0000498
00:20:51.830 --> 00:20:53.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Trying to be positive all
the time</b></Default>

c0000499
00:20:53.420 --> 00:20:54.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is exhausting, isn't it?</b></Default>

c0000500
00:20:54.920 --> 00:20:57.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You suck at comforting.
Seriously awful.</b></Default>

c0000501
00:20:58.420 --> 00:21:01.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But still,
it kind of puts me at ease.</b></Default>

c0000502
00:21:01.390 --> 00:21:05.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales]
Really, such a relief.</b></Default>

c0000503
00:21:05.930 --> 00:21:07.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales]</b></Default>

c0000504
00:21:09.600 --> 00:21:11.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So, uh...
- Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000505
00:21:12.020 --> 00:21:15.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Can I go see the fireworks
with you guys?</b></Default>

c0000506
00:21:15.230 --> 00:21:16.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sorry, no.</b></Default>

c0000507
00:21:16.360 --> 00:21:17.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000508
00:21:17.650 --> 00:21:19.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- At least not
if you ask like that.</b></Default>

c0000509
00:21:20.030 --> 00:21:21.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
I--</b></Default>

c0000510
00:21:21.780 --> 00:21:23.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanna see the fireworks, too.</b></Default>

c0000511
00:21:23.660 --> 00:21:25.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm not the person
you should be asking.</b></Default>

c0000512
00:21:25.450 --> 00:21:26.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh?
- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000513
00:21:26.990 --> 00:21:27.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000514
00:21:35.710 --> 00:21:36.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's me.</b></Default>

c0000515
00:21:38.760 --> 00:21:41.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.
I met up with Azusagawa.</b></Default>

c0000516
00:21:42.010 --> 00:21:45.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And, well, I have--
I have a favor to ask you.</b></Default>

c0000517
00:21:47.260 --> 00:21:48.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inhales sharply]</b></Default>

c0000518
00:21:48.850 --> 00:21:50.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanna go see the fireworks
together with you guys.</b></Default>

c0000519
00:21:50.940 --> 00:21:52.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[receiver thuds]
- Huh?</b></Default>

c0000520
00:21:56.320 --> 00:21:58.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps approaching]</b></Default>

c0000521
00:22:03.160 --> 00:22:04.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hello?</b></Default>

c0000522
00:22:04.700 --> 00:22:05.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I think you should head back</b></Default>

c0000523
00:22:05.780 --> 00:22:07.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to the consultation room now.</b></Default>

c0000524
00:22:07.950 --> 00:22:10.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakurajima's been waiting
for you there, right?</b></Default>

c0000525
00:22:10.540 --> 00:22:12.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're back
to being one person.</b></Default>

c0000526
00:22:12.080 --> 00:22:14.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah.
Anyway, about the fireworks.</b></Default>

c0000527
00:22:15.290 --> 00:22:16.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't you dare be late.
Got it?</b></Default>

c0000528
00:22:16.670 --> 00:22:17.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I got it.</b></Default>

c0000529
00:22:18.500 --> 00:22:21.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000530
00:22:21.420 --> 00:22:23.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [laughing]</b></Default>

c0000531
00:22:23.340 --> 00:22:24.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey!</b></Default>

c0000532
00:22:24.470 --> 00:22:25.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Over here, Futaba!</b></Default>

c0000533
00:22:26.850 --> 00:22:28.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Switched back to glasses, huh?</b></Default>

c0000534
00:22:28.560 --> 00:22:30.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Is it weird?</b></Default>

c0000535
00:22:30.100 --> 00:22:31.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- They go well with the yukata.</b></Default>

c0000536
00:22:31.600 --> 00:22:32.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right, Sakuta?</b></Default>

c0000537
00:22:32.890 --> 00:22:34.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Kinda erotic.</b></Default>

c0000538
00:22:34.770 --> 00:22:36.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right, Kunimi?
- Can't deny that.</b></Default>

c0000539
00:22:37.400 --> 00:22:39.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And this
is why I hated yukatas.</b></Default>

c0000540
00:22:42.700 --> 00:22:45.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[distant fireworks booming]</b></Default>

c0000541
00:22:50.740 --> 00:22:51.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kunimi.</b></Default>

c0000542
00:22:51.910 --> 00:22:53.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000543
00:22:54.420 --> 00:22:55.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What?</b></Default>

c0000544
00:22:58.630 --> 00:22:59.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000545
00:23:02.920 --> 00:23:05.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Futaba. I, uh...</b></Default>

c0000546
00:23:05.380 --> 00:23:08.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Don't bother answering me.
I already know.</b></Default>

c0000547
00:23:08.300 --> 00:23:09.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Got it.</b></Default>

c0000548
00:23:09.560 --> 00:23:10.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If you said anything,</b></Default>

c0000549
00:23:10.850 --> 00:23:13.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm pretty sure that
I'd start crying.</b></Default>

c0000550
00:23:13.310 --> 00:23:16.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If you do I'm sure Sakuta will
lend you a sleeve of his yukata.</b></Default>

c0000551
00:23:16.480 --> 00:23:17.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Even if you're snotty.</b></Default>

c0000552
00:23:17.900 --> 00:23:19.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [chuckles]
Idiot.</b></Default>

c0000553
00:23:19.650 --> 00:23:20.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales]</b></Default>

c0000554
00:23:22.280 --> 00:23:24.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kunimi?
- Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000555
00:23:24.490 --> 00:23:26.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Go make up
with your girlfriend already.</b></Default>

c0000556
00:23:26.450 --> 00:23:29.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure the reason is me
or Azusagawa, isn't it?</b></Default>

c0000557
00:23:29.490 --> 00:23:30.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah.</b></Default>

c0000558
00:23:31.080 --> 00:23:33.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess I'll give her
a call later.</b></Default>

c0000559
00:23:35.120 --> 00:23:36.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [sniffles]</b></Default>

c0000560
00:23:38.670 --> 00:23:41.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

c0000561
00:23:41.710 --> 00:23:44.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>["Fukashigi no Carte" plays]</b></Default>

c0000562
00:23:44.630 --> 00:23:51.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000563
00:24:30.340 --> 00:24:37.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000564
00:24:38.230 --> 00:24:41.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cell phone vibrating
and ringing]</b></Default>

c0000565
00:24:43.070 --> 00:24:46.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groaning]</b></Default>

c0000566
00:24:49.740 --> 00:24:51.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000567
00:24:53.160 --> 00:24:54.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000568
00:24:55.870 --> 00:25:00.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, Sakuta.
You're such a rascal.</b></Default>

